Text:
@trakintech 
Apse or apki team ke liye ek challange hai is phone ke camera mai specially 
Raw expert mein long exposures of photo click hoti hai to photo click karne ke bad jab uska Ham video dekhte hain vah kuchh processing karta hai aur blackout kar deta hai photo ko aur exposure mein bahut gadbad karta hai especially tab hota Hai jab aap 8 second ke exposure se upar jaate Hain tab hota hai jabki yah raw expert app ke update ke aane ke bad hua Hai usse pahle raw expert mein jo Ham photo click karte The vah sahi aaya karte The jabki Ham vahi setting Jo uska  ka apna default camera mein hai usmein vahi Pro setting rakhte Hain to vah photo Jaisi aani chahie Jaise mujhko chahie vaisi photo mujhe milati Hai lekin raw expert mein kya hota hai ki photo click karne ke bad 20 second ki ya 15 second ki photo jo hoti hai usmein vah lights ko white Kar dega Baki Dal Kar dega samajh mein nahin aata hai kya chij hai

Translated:
@trakintech 
There is a challenge for yourself or your team, especially with your phone's camera. 
Long exposures of photo click happens in Raw expert after clicking the photo. When we watch the video, it does a lot of processing and blackouts the photo and makes a lot of mess in the exposure, especially when you go beyond 8 second exposure. This tab happens after the update of Raw expert app. This is the first time in Raw expert that we click the photo. The same setting is there in my default camera, I mean I keep the same Pro setting to get the photo as I want, I get the photo as I want, but what happens in the raw expert is that after clicking the photo, I get a photo of 20 seconds or 15 seconds, I turn the lights to white, then what is the matter?

